    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessemus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/186" key="#Princeps">Sicardus</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3629" key="#Other_palatine_officer">Aionis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">stolesaiz</rs> nostro, tibi <persName
                            key="#Gold #Specialized_workers" ref="#people/3633">Autulo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gold #Specialized_workers">aurife</rs> nostro <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Confiscation #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >omnem rem quam <name ref="Allo">Allo</name> conparavit a <rs
                                key="#Slave">servi</rs> nostri palatii fine precepto</rs> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/3464"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                            >Folianense</placeName>, de <rs key="#Marepahis">maripansato</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3630" key="#Marepahis">Roffrid</persName>, et <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >casellas</rs> nostri palatii quam tenuit <name
                            ref="Sarnipertus iocolarius">Sarnipertus</name>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">iocolarius</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation">sine
                        precepto</rs>, ipse vero Sarniperto defunctus est, in ea videlicet ratione
                        ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum predicta omnia que
                        superius legitur tu et heredes tui possideatis, et a nullo ex nostris
                        iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus
                        habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod
                        vero preceptum concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego
                            <persName ref="#people/3462" key="#Writer">Theodericus</persName>. Actum
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> sexto
                        anno, mense ianuario, prima indictio. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
